Cross compile and install:
  - setup cross compile environment
  - downloads can be found at https://curl.haxx.se/download.html
  - extract files
  - configure the cross compile, build, and install
    - $ cd curl-7.52.1
    - $ ./configure --prefix=/home/rasppi_xcompile/extra_libs_install/curl --host=arm-linux-gnueabihf --with-sysroot=/home/rasppi_xcompile/sysroot --enable-static=no
    - $ make
    - $ make install => this installs files to /home/rasppi_xcompile/extra_libs_install/
    - move the header and library files out of any sub-directories